<item>
            <title>[LU-19339] kernel update [RHEL 9.6 5.14.0-570.42.2.el9_6]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19339</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) for kernel 5.14.0-570.41.1.el9_6:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: udmabuf: fix a buf size overflow issue during udmabuf creation (CVE-2025-37803)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: idpf: convert control queue mutex to a spinlock (CVE-2025-38392)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:15429&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:15429&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) for kernel 5.14.0-570.44.1.el9_6:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ipv6: mcast: Delay put pmc-&amp;gt;idev in mld_del_delrec() (CVE-2025-38550)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:15740&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:15740&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
